      <title>印尼明年将提高增值税，并提供优惠措施缓解冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/indonesia-goes-ahead-with-vat-hike-offers-perks-to-soften-blow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼将在2025年继续提高增值税，同时提供一系列激励措施以减轻对消费和经济增长的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/indonesia-goes-ahead-with-vat-hike-offers-perks-to-soften-blow</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 05:26:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
